Quick Reference - remedytech.zone

To preview and manage the remedytech.zone project locally:

Download the Code:
Download the singular index.html file provided in this workspace. Ensure your image assets (e.g., Copilot_20260526_230730.png) are in the same folder.

Open in Browser:
Double-click index.html to open it in Chrome, Safari, or Edge. No backend server is required due to the CDN-powered Tailwind architecture.

Editing Data & Affiliate Links:
Open index.html in your text editor. Scroll down to the <script> section. Locate eCommerceAssets. Modify affiliateUrl, price, or img parameters to hot-swap products instantly.

Testing UI Components:

Click the Left/Right arrows on the product sliders to test smooth-scroll snapping.

Click "See More Products" to verify the comprehensive grid modal.

Click any individual product card to launch the deep-dive modal and verify the "Buy on Amazon" redirect paths.
